10 evam eva mugdhavān ārtasya vācā,
11 yathā, api ca ayam tāmrātmakaḥ āsīt,
12 tathāpi sa duḥkhena viddha iva ābhāsate sma;

22 yadyapi aham āgataḥ syām kimcid vilambena,
23 mā te viṣādaḥ astu mama saha samvāde;
24 paśya yathā mama na viṣādaḥ asti, aham ca dagdhaḥ asmi!

28 bruhi me kim Romaṇyāḥ śāntim vā vigraham vā kurvanti;
29 aham hi tataḥ parvateṣu āsam madhye Urbino
30 evaṃ ca girer yataḥ Tiberasya udgamaḥ asti."

37 tava Romagna na asti, na ca kadācit āsīt,
38 yasyāḥ svāmīnāṃ hṛdayeṣu yuddham vinā;
39 atha ca adhunā tatra api na kaścid viśrāntaḥ mayā sthāpitaḥ.

55 Adya kaḥ asi, tvām prārthayāmi yathā naḥ kathāḥ;
56 mā bhūr duro 'nyebhyaḥ adhikaḥ,
57 yadi tava nāma loke śiro dhārayati.

61 "Yadi aham manyeya mama uttaraṃ syāt
62 tasya puruṣasya yaḥ kadācit punar āgacchet loke,
63 ayam jvālā tiṣṭhet aparaiḥ kampanaiḥ vinā;

67 Aham āsīṃ yodhaḥ, tataś ca abhūvaṃ vairagya-vān,
68 manyamānaḥ evam saṃyuktaḥ kuryām prāyaścittam;
69 caityaṃ ca mama viśvāsaḥ āgamiṣyati pūrṇaḥ,

70 yadi na abhavat mahān yaja-patiḥ, yasmai dur-gatiḥ prajāyātām!,
71 yaḥ mām punar api prathamam apradham ānayati sma;
72 katham ca kena ca, icchāmi yathā mām vijānīyāt.

82 yat pūrvam mama priyam āsīt, tadā mama duḥkham ajāyata,
83 tataś ca aham anutāpī ca prāyaścittakṛt ca abhūvam;
84 ahaṃ durdaivīnaḥ! tat ca upakārī syāt.

97 Svasya garvāgnidāhasya parimokṣāya;
98 Prāśnaṃ cakāra mām, aham tu maunaṃ babhūva,
99 Yataḥ tasya vacaṃsi madamayīni pratyabhāsanta.

100 Atha punar abravīt: “Tava hṛdayam mā viṣṇuyāt;
101 Adhunā tvām amocayāmi, tvam ca māṃ śikṣaya
102 Yathā tvam Penestrinum bhūmau apatakṣīḥ.”

115 Avaśyamayaṃ mama durātmabhiḥ saha adhastanaṃ prāptavyaḥ
116 yataḥ ayam mithyā-upadeśaṃ dadau,
117 yasmāt kālāt ahaṃ asya keśeṣu vartate;

124 Sa māṃ Minosam nayati sma; sa ca aṣṭau vāram
125 puccham āsya kaṭhinam parivartayati sma;
126 tataś ca yadā sa mahān krodhāt tam adadamśa,

127 tadā āha: “Ayaṃ agneḥ rājñām asti”;
128 tasmāt tatra yatra tvam paśyasi naṣṭaḥ asmi,
129 evam ca vastram ādāya gacchan duḥkhito 'smi.
